{"tid":895322,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"同女人講嘢千祈唔好用理性諗法","createTime":"2018-11-09T06:00:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-09T16:18:51.000Z","uid":72186,"like":40,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1b5158c00399efc34493ade42f4244b08520d7f7","tid":895322,"uid":72186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T06:00:35.000Z","msg":"同女人講嘢千祈唔好用理性諗法<br />\n啫係你永遠當佢係有精神病嘅人<br />\n用理解 耐心同佢講嘢<br />\n唔好要求佢做更多就得<br />\n你都唔會要求一個病人理你感受啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n女人個腦永遠唔係佢自己的<br />\n永遠都俾所謂 荷爾蒙影響 大上大落 諗嘢無邏輯 <br />\n成日話自己理性 但偏偏依句就係感性說話<br />\n信佢就真係毒撚青頭仔<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n做唔到上面啲嘢真係唔好拍拖 會好辛苦<br />\n叫雞會開心啲 至少明買明賣 <br />\n如果唔係課金養人哋老婆 就好唔抵 晒錢晒時間"},{"pid":"4fbb6d598a941c3ada0c2a26c970faaffa355daf","tid":895322,"uid":41315,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T06:53:25.000Z","msg":"男人同女人嗌交一定會輸<br />\n因為男人有樣先天缺陷<br />\n<br />\n就係講野一定要 make sense"},{"pid":"c7e3a65fcdc75cbc21d702c2e14155e8bd585d6e","tid":895322,"uid":155818,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T06:54:20.000Z","msg":"對唔住我錯啦原諒我啦 呢D基本野先講左先"},{"pid":"10acca7ce4b773eecac6b5b2e484a541a2421938","tid":895322,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T06:55:41.000Z","msg":"aggal"},{"pid":"b43f2e80d24a4d5b96d74bdecbb278dc4790f49a","tid":895322,"uid":207254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T06:57:24.000Z","msg":"好似太遲先領悟到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d67b1af726b32bd210e39ef466d47e10bbb8109","tid":895322,"uid":177572,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T06:57:53.000Z","msg":"呢個世界有兩種女人<br />\n<br />\n1. 唔理性既女人<br />\n2. 以為自己理性既女人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2942be5bf6e699f021daf313ee98df696fa45bbb","tid":895322,"uid":4179,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"c7e3a65f